			<h1>About the game</h1>
			<hr />
			<p>Text Adventure is a community built story. Users can adventure through story like a game, where they can choose paths which will lead to different events. These choices are created completely by the community and can be played by anyone who visits the website. 
			Anyone can play and be able to decide their own path in the story.  You must be a user to be able to make contribution to the community tree by creating nodes. Nodes can be up voted as well as down voted.  In the case of any inappropriate content is posted an administrator will be able take care of it.
			The user also has the choice to view the community tree as a whole and jump directly to a node they left off at. They can also hover over a node to preview before making a final decision on where they want to start their part of the story.
			Most importantly enjoy and have fun.</p>
